# File Structure

- `composables/` → Vue reactive helpers (useX, getX)
- `lib/` → Pure utilities (formatters, ui-helpers, api)
- `components/ui/` → shadcn-vue (don't edit)
- `components/shared/` → Reusable (`NetCard`, `OperatorCard`)
- `components/[feature]/` → Feature-specific

**Existing**: `getAvatarUrl`, `formatDateTime`, `formatCallSign`, `getRoleBadgeClass`

**Always use yarn**, never npm
